## How to propose a change

The guides are **living**. When a new bug, ADR, or convention crystallises a pattern:

1. Add it as a MUST/SHOULD rule in the right guide under `.agentic/guides/`.
2. Quote the bug, migration, or commit it came from in the *Why*.
3. PR title: `docs(patterns): <rule short title>`.
4. Owner reviews — patterns are the spec, not a draft. Only the owner can approve
   removing or weakening a rule.
